<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Puppy" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Puppy,</orth> a young dog, a whelp: <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.4.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. IV, 4, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 5, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.1.175" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 1, 175</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.3.341" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 3, 341</bibl>. Adjectively: <emph>a p. dog</emph> == a new-born dog, <bibl n="shak. jn 2.460" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 460</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.2.78" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 2, 78</bibl>. <cit><quote>a p. greyhound,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.107" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 107</bibl></cit>. Term of contempt, implying stupidity: <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.726" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 726</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.4.30" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 4, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.2.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 2, 22</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>